menu "Platform selection"

config ARCH_CANOE
	bool "Enable support for Qualcomm Technologies, Inc. Canoe"
	depends on ARCH_QCOM
	help
	  This enables support for Qualcomm Technologies, Inc. Canoe
	  chipset. If you do not wish to build a kernel that runs on this
	  chipset or if you are unsure, say 'N' here.

